nodes.text: Enarc was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Mid Rim. During the Trade Federation blockade of the planet Naboo leading up to their invasion, Governor Kelma of Karlinus sent an agricultural transport full of grain to Naboo as a sign of good faith due to the recent summit, but the starship was refused passage and was forced to divert to Enarc, where the grain cargo was placed in cold storage.
